cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper is about video captioning, which involves understanding visual content and generating natural language descriptions. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The proposed model also involves iterative refinement, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper evaluates its method on video captioning benchmarks (cs.MM), which further supports the above sub-categories.
